NT Phylogenies

Crock

01/10/2021

Figures

These figures include a number of trees with heatmaps depicting the presence/absence of virulence and resistance genes in Staphylococcus argenteus. They are organised by clonal complex.

ST1850

tree_1850 <- read.beast("1850_timemccCA.tree")
tips_1850 <- read.delim("1850_names.txt")
nwk_1850 <- read.newick("1850_timemccCA.nwk")
tree_1850 <- rename_taxa(tree_1850, tips_1850, label, new)
nwk_1850 <- rename_taxa(nwk_1850, tips_1850, label, new)

#geography data
geography_1850 <- read.delim("1850_geo.txt", na.strings = "")
geoH_1850 <- read.delim("1850_geoH.txt", na.strings ="")
   rownames(geoH_1850) <- nwk_1850$tip.label

   #res data
   res_1850 <- read.delim("1850_res.txt")
            rownames(res_1850) <- nwk_1850$tip.label

p1850 <- ggtree(tree_1850, mrsd="2012-06-01") %<+% geography_1850 +
      theme_tree2() +
      #geom_tiplab(size=0.7) +
      geom_tippoint(aes(color=Region), size=3, alpha=1, na.rm=TRUE) +
      scale_discrete_manual(name="Region", values=c("#363C91","#6F9283", "#F69C3F", "#756D54", "#BED558"),
                            aesthetics=c("color")) +
      ggtitle("C")   
   #theme(legend.position = "none")
      #labs(title="ST1850 Phylogeny (BEAST)")

p1850

#Global region heatmap
p1850a <- ggtree(tree_1850, mrsd="2012-06-01") +
      theme_tree2() +
      scale_x_ggtree(breaks=c(1985, 2000,2015), labels=c(1985, 2000, 2015)) +
      geom_tiplab(size=2) +
      labs(x="Time (years)")


p1850a <- gheatmap(p1850a, geoH_1850, width=0.04, offset=2.25, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_manual(name="Region", guide=guide_legend(order=1),
                           values= c("#984ea3","#ffff33"),
                           breaks= c("Australia","Oceania"))



#resistance heatmap
p1850r <- p1850a + new_scale_fill()

p1850r <- gheatmap(p1850r, res_1850, width=0.16, offset=3.5, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_manual(name="Acquired resistance genes", guide=guide_legend(order=2),
                           values= c("#A72608", "#D6300A",
                                     "#016EB7",
                                     "#FFA91F",
                                     "white"),
                           breaks= c("blaZ", "mecA",
                                     "qacA",
                                     "erm(C)",
                                     "absent")) +
         ggtitle("Presence of Acquired Resistance Genes in the ST1850 Clonal Complex", "Time-scaled MCC tree from Bayesian analysis")
p1850r

#ggsave("1850res_tree.svg", p1850r, scale=1.5)
#ggsave("1850_NTtree.svg", p1850, width=18.5, height=18.5, units="cm")

ST2198

#tree setup
tree_2198 <- read.beast("2198_timemccCA.tree")
tips_2198 <- read.delim("2198_names.txt")
nwk_2198 <- read.newick("2198_timemccCA.nwk")
tree_2198 <- rename_taxa(tree_2198, tips_2198, label, new)
nwk_2198 <- rename_taxa(nwk_2198, tips_2198, label, new)

#geography data
geography_2198 <- read.delim("2198_geo.txt", na.strings = "")
geoH_2198 <- read.delim("2198_geoH.txt", na.strings ="")
   rownames(geoH_2198) <- nwk_2198$tip.label

   #res data
   res_2198 <- read.delim("2198_res.txt")
            rownames(res_2198) <- nwk_2198$tip.label
   
   
#NT Tree
p2198 <- ggtree(tree_2198, mrsd="2019-11-09") %<+% geography_2198 +
      theme_tree2()+
      #geom_tiplab(size=0.7)+
      geom_tippoint(aes(color=Region), size=3, alpha=1, na.rm=TRUE) +
      scale_discrete_manual(name="Region",
                            values=c("#930F32", "#363C91", "#F69C3F","#6F9283", "#67C4CB", "#BED558"),
                            aesthetics=c("color"))+
      ggtitle("C")

#Global region heatmap
p2198a <- ggtree(tree_2198, mrsd="2019-11-09") +
      theme_tree2() +
      scale_x_ggtree(breaks=c(1985, 2000,2020), labels=c(1985, 2000, 2020)) +
      geom_tiplab(size=2) +
      labs(x="Time (years)")


p2198a <- gheatmap(p2198a, geoH_2198, width=0.04, offset=2, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_brewer(name="Region", guide=guide_legend(order=1), palette="Set1")



#resistance heatmap
p2198r <- p2198a + new_scale_fill()

p2198r <- gheatmap(p2198r, res_2198, width=0.12, offset=3.5, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_manual(name="Acquired resistance genes", guide=guide_legend(order=2),
                           values= c("#A72608", "#D6300A",
                                     "#FFA91F",
                                     "white"),
                           breaks= c("blaZ", "mecA",
                                     "erm(C)",
                                     "absent")) +
         ggtitle("Presence of Acquired Resistance Genes in the ST2198 Clonal Complex", "Time-scaled MCC tree from Bayesian analysis")
p2198r

tree_1223 <- read.beast("1223_timemccCA.tree")
tips_1223 <- read.delim("1223_names.txt")
nwk_1223 <- read.newick("1223_timemccCA.nwk")
tree_1223 <- rename_taxa(tree_1223, tips_1223, label, new)
nwk_1223 <- rename_taxa(nwk_1223, tips_1223, label, new)

#tiporder_1223 <- as.data.frame(nwk_1223$tip.label)
#write.csv(file="1223_tiporder.csv", tiporder_1223)

geoH_1223 <- read.delim("1223_geoH.txt", na.strings ="")
   geoH_1223 <- as.data.frame(geoH_1223$Region)
   colnames(geoH_1223) <- "Region"
   rownames(geoH_1223) <- nwk_1223$tip.label
res_1223 <- read.delim("1223_res.txt")
            rownames(res_1223) <- nwk_1223$tip.label


geography_1223 <- read.delim("1223_geo.txt", na.strings = "")


p1223 <- ggtree(tree_1223, mrsd="2019-12-27") %<+% geography_1223 +
      theme_tree2()+
      #geom_tiplab(size=2) +
      geom_tippoint(aes(color=Region), size=3, alpha=1, na.rm=TRUE) +
      scale_discrete_manual(name="Region",
                            values=c("#930F32", "#363C91", "#F69C3F","#6F9283", "#756D54"),
                            aesthetics=c("color")) +
      ggtitle("C")

p1223

#ggsave("1223_NTtree.svg", p1223, width=18.5, height=18.5, units="cm")

p1223a <- ggtree(tree_1223, mrsd="2019-12-27") +
      theme_tree2() +
      scale_x_ggtree(breaks=c(1825, 1850,1900, 1950, 2000, 2021), labels=c(1825, 1850, 1900, 1950, 2000, 2021)) +
      geom_tiplab(size=2) +
      labs(x="Time (years)")

p1223a <- gheatmap(p1223a, geoH_1223, width=0.04, offset=14, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_manual(name="Region", guide=guide_legend(order=1),
                           values= c("#377eb8", "#4daf4a", "#94d49f", "#984ea3", "#ff7f00", "#ffff33", "white"),
                           breaks= c("Americas", "Asia", "Asia (Thailand)", "Australia", "Europe", "Oceania", "NA")) 


p1223r <- p1223a + new_scale_fill()

p1223r <- gheatmap(p1223r, res_1223, width=0.2, offset=23, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_manual(name="Acquired resistance genes", guide=guide_legend(order=2),
                           values= c("#A72608", "#D6300A",
                                     "#24A899",
                                     "#CCE2A3",
                                     "#73BF7F",
                                     "white"),
                           breaks= c("blaZ", "mecA",
                                     "tet(K)",
                                     "lnu(A)",
                                     "str",
                                     "absent")) +
         ggtitle("Presence of Acquired Resistance Genes in the ST1223 Clonal Complex", "Time-scaled MCC tree from Bayesian analysis")

ST2250

tree_2250nwk <- read.newick("2250_timemccCA3k.nwk")
tree_2250 <- read.beast("2250_timemccCA3k.tree")
tips_2250 <- read.delim("2250_names.txt")

tree_2250 <- rename_taxa(tree_2250, tips_2250, label, new)
tree_2250nwk <- rename_taxa(tree_2250nwk, tips_2250, label, new)
geography_2250 <- read.delim("2250_geo2.txt", na.strings = "")
geoH_2250 <- read.delim("2250_geoH.txt", na.strings ="")
   geoH_2250 <- as.data.frame(geoH_2250$Region)
   colnames(geoH_2250) <- "Region"
   rownames(geoH_2250) <- tree_2250nwk$tip.label
gpa_2250 <- read.delim("2250_gpa.txt")
           rownames(gpa_2250) <- tree_2250nwk$tip.label
res_2250 <- read.delim("2250_res.txt")
            rownames(res_2250) <- tree_2250nwk$tip.label


p2250 <- ggtree(tree_2250, mrsd="2019-12-31") + #%<+% geography_2250 +
      theme_tree2()+
      scale_x_ggtree(breaks=c(1825, 1850,1900, 1950, 2000, 2021), labels=c(1825, 1850, 1900, 1950, 2000, 2021)) +
      geom_tiplab(size=1.25) +
      labs(x="Time (years)")
           #+
      #geom_tippoint(aes(color=Region), size=2, alpha=1, na.rm=TRUE) +
      #scale_fill_brewer("Country")
      #scale_colour_brewer(name="Region", palette="Set1", aesthetics=c("color"))

p2250 <- gheatmap(p2250, geoH_2250, width=0.02, offset=9, colnames=FALSE) +
         scale_fill_manual(name="Region", guide=guide_legend(order=1),
                           values= c("#377eb8", "#4daf4a", "#94d49f", "#984ea3", "#ff7f00", "#ffff33", "white"),
                           breaks= c("Americas", "Asia", "Asia (Thailand)", "Australia", "Europe", "Oceania", "NA")) 

p2250a <- p2250 + new_scale_fill()

p2250a <- gheatmap(p2250a, gpa_2250, width=0.1, offset=13, colnames=FALSE) +
            scale_fill_manual(name="Genes of interest", guide=guide_legend(order=2),
                              values= c("#E23428", "#7A1F00",
                                        "#34AD6C","#51B93C","#AAC705",
                                 "white"),
                              breaks =c("lukED", "lukFS-PV",
                                        "sec", "sel", "tst",
                                 "absent")) +
            ggtitle("Presence of Virulence Genes of Interest in the ST2250 Clonal Complex", "Time-scaled MCC tree from Bayesian analysis")

p2250a
